PrecisThe ATOMIC ENERGY CONTROL BOARD COST RECOVERY FEES REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the remission of a portion of the fees when a licence is cancelled prior to its expiry, where the status of a facility or its activities change and the fees for that are lower, or where the fees for a licence are reduced.
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 1994-0039 Publication Date: 1994-04-20
Attachments
precis:
The ATOMIC ENERGY CONTROL BOARD COST RECOVERY FEES REMISSION ORDER - which
provides for the remission of a portion of the fees when a licence is
cancelled prior to its expiry, where the status of a facility or its
activities change and the fees for that are lower, or where the fees for a
licence are reduced.
